@startuml
actor Admin
participant "Home Page" as HomePage
participant "Role Page" as RolePage
participant System
database Database

== View Roles ==
Admin -> HomePage : Click on Role Tab
activate HomePage
HomePage -> RolePage : Display role page
deactivate HomePage

activate RolePage
RolePage -> System : Call API to get roles
activate System
System -> Database : Fetch role list
activate Database
Database --> System : Return role list
deactivate Database
System --> RolePage : Return role data
deactivate System
RolePage --> Admin : Display role list
deactivate RolePage

alt if error
    activate System
    System --> Admin : Show error message
    deactivate System
end
@enduml
